text: The twelfth cycle of Holland's Next Top Model premiered on 2 September 2019 on RTL5. Anna Nooshin reprised the role the show's host. The panel of judges was again composed of cycle 2 winner Kim Feenstra and photographer Nigel Barker. JeanPaul Paula did not return, in his place there will be a different guest judge each week.
